      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "チケット完売だって、怜ちゃん",
      "startTime": 2.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-mei001.wav",
      "text": "私達二人だけだから心配してたけど、よかったね！",
      "startTime": 5.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei001.wav",
      "text": "うん。よかった",
      "startTime": 9.466666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "芽衣もいろんな人呼んじゃったから",
      "startTime": 11.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-mei002.wav",
      "text": "もしガラガラだったらどうしよって思ってたんだ～",
      "startTime": 14.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei002.wav",
      "text": "うん。よかったね",
      "startTime": 18.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-mei003.wav",
      "text": "……怜ちゃん？　ねえねえ、聞いてる？",
      "startTime": 20.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……え？",
      "startTime": 25.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei003.wav",
      "text": "……うん、聞いてる",
      "startTime": 26.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きっと怜ちゃんのご両親も来てくれるよ",
      "startTime": 29.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-mei004.wav",
      "text": "……チケットは渡せたんだよね？",
      "startTime": 33.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei004.wav",
      "text": "渡すことは、出来たわ",
      "startTime": 36.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei005.wav",
      "text": "お父さん、私のライブに来てほしいの",
      "startTime": 41.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "0",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad001.wav",
      "text": "何度も言わせるな",
      "startTime": 44.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は、お前の仕事を認めてはいないと――",
      "startTime": 47.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私、決めた。お父さんが来てくれるまで、何度でも誘う",
      "startTime": 50.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei006.wav",
      "text": "来てくれるまで、絶対にアイドルを辞めない",
      "startTime": 56.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad002.wav",
      "text": "……怜",
      "startTime": 59.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お父さんが反対する理由も、分かる",
      "startTime": 60.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei007.wav",
      "text": "間違ってるとも思わない。心配してくれてありがとう",
      "startTime": 64.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad003.wav",
      "text": "そう思うなら……",
      "startTime": 69.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも……一つだけ言わせて……",
      "startTime": 71,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei008.wav",
      "text": "アイドルだって……誰かを救うことが出来るの！",
      "startTime": 75.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自意識過剰かもしれない。でも、私達のために",
      "startTime": 79.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei009.wav",
      "text": "お金や時間を使って会いに来てくれる人がいるんだよ？",
      "startTime": 84.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "会えてよかったって。明日から頑張れるって",
      "startTime": 88.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei010.wav",
      "text": "そう言ってくれるの。それが私の……希望にもなるの！",
      "startTime": 92.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "0",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad004.wav",
      "text": "……続けたところで、成功する訳がない",
      "startTime": 98.16666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうかもしれない",
      "startTime": 102.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei011.wav",
      "text": "でも、成功してもしなくても、私は続ける",
      "startTime": 104.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad005.wav",
      "text": "……いつかはアイドルを辞める日が来るだろう",
      "startTime": 109.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その先はどうするつもりだ！",
      "startTime": 112.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――今は分からない",
      "startTime": 117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei012.wav",
      "text": "毎日、目の前のことを頑張るだけで精一杯だから",
      "startTime": 119.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、私はアイドルになって、よかったと思う",
      "startTime": 123.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei013.wav",
      "text": "今が人生で一番、充実してる。絶対に後悔しない",
      "startTime": 128.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad006.wav",
      "text": "そんな甘い考えで、幸せになれるはずがない！",
      "startTime": 133.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうして私の言うことが聞けないんだ！！",
      "startTime": 137.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "逆らってごめんなさい、お父さん",
      "startTime": 139.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei014.wav",
      "text": "でも、私の幸せは、私が決めたいの。それに――",
      "startTime": 143.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルを、ダンスを、夢を諦めたら",
      "startTime": 151.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
